    This paragraph should be parsed as a nested Beanstalk template inside the implicit `$markdown` body.
]

[$doc:
    ## Documentation comment

    This should highlight like `$markdown`, including `inline code`.

    [codeblock, $code("bst"):
        import @docs {
            pages/home {render as render_home},
            pages/about {content as about_content},
        }
    ]
]

